ice. We have been able to synthesize from mono to few atomic\nlayers of free standing stanene and characterize them optically using UV-Vis\nabsorption, Raman and photoluminescence spectroscopy. First principles\ncalculations have been performed to interpret experimental results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2015 16:08:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
