s is pointed out. To complement the\ndiscussion, all possible (spin 0 and 1) leptoquark models are matched to the\nlow-energy field theory so that the effective analysis can be used to survey\nthese candidates for new physics. These models also serve as concrete examples\nwhere the hypotheses of this work can be implemented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2015 20:09:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-21"}
