ng theories: the excess energy density produced is\nexpected to diverge for scaling dimensions $\\Delta > d/2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 May 2015 02:03:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2015 19:14:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-30"}
