l galactic merging of the system and the\nonset of cooling in the shock-heated core could account for the observed lack\nof well-developed cool cores in some fossil groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2015 20:00:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-22"}
